title: Commercial Drivers needed to drive newer company trucks.
text:
Commercial Drivers needed to drive newer company trucks. ad date: 10/24/2015 
Commercial Drivers needed to drive newer company trucks. Class A CDL and passing drug test are required. Trips will mostly be down to SF or up to the Astoria area. Compensation based on trip. Please inquire in person at Alber Seafoods plant in Crescent City Harbor or by email to jobs@alberseafoods.com
